The program may run into time problems, i.e. the program
exceeds the remaining time.

Sometimes, moves of the computer which mate are regarded as
illegal moves, i.e. the program makes the move (winning the
game) and then states this move as illegal (king in check).

After creating the binary book file, the program 
ends unexpectedly with stack frame overflow. 
Therefore, you have to type "make install" twice.
This happens on an apollo workstations, and I am not shure
about it on other platforms.
